Package: spHelper
Type: Package
Title: Extension of Package `hyperSpec` and Various Convenience Functions
Description: Functions that extend capabilities of package `hyperSpec` (e.g.,
            plotting, preprocessing, simulation). Functions to visualize
            spectroscopic differences and classification results. Various
            convenience and wrapper functions, R operators as well as
            RStudio addins.
